1
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:34,918
=Vanished Name=

2
00:01:35,192 --> 00:01:37,880
=Episode 16=
(Promises Must Be Kept)

3
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:39,640
Two?

4
00:01:40,559 --> 00:01:42,559
They invited me
to check the construction quality.

5
00:01:43,919 --> 00:01:45,399
Are you the boss here?

6
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,440
Not at all.

7
00:01:49,319 --> 00:01:52,360
They're trying to squeeze
every last drop out of me.

8
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:55,559
If you ever run into trouble here,

9
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,279
just tell me.

10
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:58,800
If I can,

11
00:01:59,199 --> 00:02:00,399
- I'll fix it.
- Two buns.

12
00:02:00,479 --> 00:02:01,399
That's great.

13
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,640
Bai Shu helps knead the dough daily.

14
00:02:04,039 --> 00:02:04,919
And you're so helpful.

15
00:02:04,919 --> 00:02:06,160
I'll get your change.

16
00:02:06,759 --> 00:02:08,559
I really can't thank you two enough.

17
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,879
I'd like one.

18
00:02:12,279 --> 00:02:13,040
Sure.

19
00:02:14,559 --> 00:02:16,279
Your daughter kneaded this herself.

20
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:18,040
Have some more.

21
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,640
You have to try them properly.

22
00:02:20,559 --> 00:02:21,679
Four buns.

23
00:02:24,159 --> 00:02:25,040
No need to pay.

24
00:02:25,119 --> 00:02:25,719
Here you go.

25
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,232
Here.

26
00:02:26,232 --> 00:02:27,119
Take them.

27
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,240
Have a good taste.

28
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,432
Put them here.

29
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:32,119
Two buns.

30
00:02:32,119 --> 00:02:32,960
Here, two.

31
00:02:33,679 --> 00:02:34,360
How many for you?

32
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:34,879
Two too.

33
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,599
Two, perfect.

34
00:02:35,599 --> 00:02:36,879
Thanks for caring for Bai Shu.

35
00:02:37,399 --> 00:02:39,040
It's Bai Shu who has been caring for us.

36
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,920
She often comes by to help.

37
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:43,439
Our place is a mess.
But she doesn't mind.

38
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:45,360
Upon arriving, she mops and tidies up.

39
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,360
You've raised your daughter so well.

40
00:02:47,999 --> 00:02:48,520
Exact change.

41
00:02:48,679 --> 00:02:50,119
Wait, one more. You're short one.

42
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:54,480
Bai Shu and Xiaoming are good friends.
It's only right.

43
00:02:54,679 --> 00:02:55,599
They're really close.

44
00:02:56,119 --> 00:02:57,399
I really like your daughter too.

45
00:02:57,559 --> 00:02:59,760
I treat your daughter as my own.

46
00:03:03,399 --> 00:03:05,360
Fifty cents each. Not five yuan.

47
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,879
Thank you, big boss.

48
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,480
That's your boss.

49
00:03:10,879 --> 00:03:12,240
She eats my buns too.

50
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,719
She supports my business.

51
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,719
She is your boss.

52
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:22,080
It smells so good.

53
00:03:24,839 --> 00:03:25,760
Buns every day.

54
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,119
Can we stop eating buns?

55
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,399
I'm turning into a bun.

56
00:03:28,719 --> 00:03:29,599
I like eating buns.

57
00:03:29,920 --> 00:03:31,520
Nothing tastes like your own labor.

58
00:03:31,999 --> 00:03:33,159
Yeah, aren't you sensible?

59
00:03:33,480 --> 00:03:34,559
She's more sensible.

60
00:03:34,559 --> 00:03:35,559
Am I right, Xiaofei?

61
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:37,040
Bai Shu is the most sensible.

62
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,920
A family of traitors.

63
00:03:38,999 --> 00:03:40,200
What hope is there?

64
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:43,080
Ma'am, what can I help you with?

65
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,520
No need to do anything.

66
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,800
Just standing here,
you're a beautiful sight.

67
00:03:46,999 --> 00:03:48,080
Am I right, Xiaofei?

68
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:48,952
Yes.

69
00:03:50,439 --> 00:03:53,279
Bai Shu, I saw your mom
at the construction site today.

70
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,839
She's so impressive.

71
00:03:54,839 --> 00:03:56,240
You can tell she's a big boss.

72
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,520
Your mom is really wonderful.

73
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:01,839
She also said
if I ever need anything, I can ask.

74
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,920
I don't have much nice stuff at home.

75
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,520
I'll make some bean paste buns.

76
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,879
Take them back for your mom.

77
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:09,368
What is it?

78
00:04:09,879 --> 00:04:10,480
Ma'am,

79
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:13,200
I'll definitely deliver
your bean paste buns.

80
00:04:13,439 --> 00:04:14,800
Thank you.

81
00:04:15,040 --> 00:04:15,839
Dinner's ready.

82
00:04:15,839 --> 00:04:16,760
Dinner's ready.

83
00:04:16,799 --> 00:04:17,479
Let me help.

84
00:04:17,479 --> 00:04:18,000
Okay.

85
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,359
Come on.

86
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,399
Sit down.

87
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,279
Bai Shu, sit down.

88
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:26,839
Ma'am, I can do it myself.

89
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,479
Come on.

90
00:04:27,799 --> 00:04:28,760
Get a bit of everything.

91
00:04:29,159 --> 00:04:30,279
And give a review later.

92
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:31,520
I'll do it myself, ma'am.

93
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,880
Bai Shu can handle it herself.

94
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:33,680
You just sit down.

95
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:35,000
Okay.

96
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,359
Why kick me?

97
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,080
I hate how you flatter important people.

98
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:40,839
So tacky.

99
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:42,120
I don't do that.

100
00:04:43,799 --> 00:04:45,359
Bai Shu is really pretty.

101
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,479
Not really.

102
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,760
Isn't she, Xiaofei?

103
00:04:47,799 --> 00:04:48,399
Yeah.

104
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,359
Eat up.

105
00:05:10,520 --> 00:05:11,279
Grab another tray.

106
00:05:44,719 --> 00:05:45,599
Little kitten.

107
00:05:45,799 --> 00:05:47,640
Little kitten. Little kitten.

108
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:37,560
If your mom knew you were
hanging out with me all day,

109
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,640
wouldn't she go crazy?

110
00:06:39,719 --> 00:06:40,344
It's fine.

111
00:06:40,799 --> 00:06:42,080
What do you mean, 'It's fine'?

112
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:44,000
Look at the mess.
You're still comforting me?

113
00:06:44,799 --> 00:06:46,839
Your mom will definitely
pull some stunt again.

114
00:06:49,799 --> 00:06:50,960
Maybe we should just leave.

115
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:51,839
I'll take you.

116
00:06:52,599 --> 00:06:53,320
Where to?

117
00:06:56,839 --> 00:06:57,560
Hang on a bit.

118
00:06:58,599 --> 00:07:01,080
Once I'm in college,
she can't control me anymore.

119
00:07:07,599 --> 00:07:09,719
Don't worry. I'll be okay.

120
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:11,359
Go inside.

121
00:07:11,880 --> 00:07:12,479
See you.

122
00:07:14,159 --> 00:07:14,839
Bye.

123
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:32,359
See you tomorrow.

124
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,000
(At that moment,)

125
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,719
(I had a strong premonition)

126
00:07:52,919 --> 00:07:54,599
(that we wouldn't
see each other tomorrow.)

127
00:08:17,719 --> 00:08:19,440
These are from Ren Xiaoming's mother.

128
00:08:19,799 --> 00:08:20,960
She asked me to thank you.

129
00:08:21,919 --> 00:08:22,960
She said you're nice.

130
00:08:26,479 --> 00:08:27,640
Why did you lie?

131
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:32,239
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

132
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:36,400
If you make a mistake,
you face the punishment.

133
00:08:37,519 --> 00:08:38,136
Right?

134
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,479
Don't go to class when school starts.

135
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:49,359
I'll handle your paperwork at school.

136
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:51,839
Just study at home.

137
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:56,639
It's senior year.
You want me to study at home?

138
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,280
With your grades,

139
00:08:59,519 --> 00:09:01,680
you could take the gaokao exam now.

140
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:07,719
Besides, you're not like
the other students.

141
00:09:08,479 --> 00:09:09,519
You have me backing you.

142
00:09:10,639 --> 00:09:11,560
No need to work hard.

143
00:09:12,599 --> 00:09:14,359
I've already arranged a college for you.

144
00:09:16,239 --> 00:09:19,320
I can get into college myself.
No need for you to worry.

145
00:09:22,599 --> 00:09:23,560
I'm going to study.

146
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,440
Where are my books?

147
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,080
Why are they all gone?

148
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,599
You said you went to Xinhua Bookstore
every day to read,

149
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:58,200
but you didn't go.

150
00:09:59,280 --> 00:10:02,440
So, you don't actually like reading.

151
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,719
Since you don't like it,

152
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,200
why keep the books around?

153
00:10:45,599 --> 00:10:46,800
Ren Xiaoming.

154
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,759
What did you buy?

155
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:48,759
Steamers.

156
00:10:48,999 --> 00:10:49,599
Ren Xiaoming.

157
00:10:49,759 --> 00:10:50,456
Mom.

158
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,359
Ren Xiaoming.

159
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,320
What?

160
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:54,999
Come down.

161
00:10:57,119 --> 00:10:58,080
More heavy lifting?

162
00:11:03,119 --> 00:11:03,879
Hurry up.

163
00:11:04,719 --> 00:11:05,719
Stop shouting.

164
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,200
Mom, what are these?

165
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,519
These are steamers and a wind stove.

166
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:11,879
For steaming big buns.

167
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:23,479
You just started making money,
and you borrowed to buy these?

168
00:11:23,479 --> 00:11:24,519
What if you lose money?

169
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:26,160
How else can I expand production?

170
00:11:26,839 --> 00:11:29,040
How else can I make money
grow into more money?

171
00:11:31,239 --> 00:11:32,239
Watch these for me.

172
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:33,320
Go quickly.

173
00:11:48,280 --> 00:11:50,119
Eat up. They're all yours.

174
00:12:00,599 --> 00:12:01,200
Is it good?

175
00:12:02,479 --> 00:12:03,080
It's good.

176
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,320
You treat another like your mom.

177
00:12:15,639 --> 00:12:17,519
You think their food tastes good.

178
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:19,999
Then eat it every day

179
00:12:20,719 --> 00:12:21,759
and every meal.

180
00:12:23,519 --> 00:12:24,160
Okay.

181
00:12:37,839 --> 00:12:39,080
Torturing yourself like this,

182
00:12:40,879 --> 00:12:41,800
is it fun?

183
00:12:51,719 --> 00:12:52,359
Li Meng.

184
00:12:53,719 --> 00:12:55,320
Xiaoming, what's up?

185
00:12:55,719 --> 00:12:56,359
Where's Bai Shu?

186
00:12:56,719 --> 00:12:57,400
Bai Shu?

187
00:12:58,599 --> 00:13:01,200
The teacher said her mom
took long-term sick leave for her.

188
00:13:04,160 --> 00:13:05,560
For how long?

189
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,879
I don't know that.

190
00:13:07,200 --> 00:13:08,759
Anyway, her stuff was taken home.

191
00:13:11,479 --> 00:13:12,952
Alright, thanks.

192
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,320
No problem. See you.

193
00:13:19,119 --> 00:13:20,080
Ren Xiaoming.

194
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,280
Ma'am.

195
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,879
(School spirit)
The finance office keeps bugging me.

196
00:13:24,119 --> 00:13:25,960
School started half a month ago.

197
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:28,280
You haven't paid this semester's
sponsorship fee.

198
00:13:28,479 --> 00:13:29,239
Hurry your mom up.

199
00:13:29,719 --> 00:13:30,359
Ma'am,

200
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:32,839
if I don't attend school,

201
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,456
can I still take the gaokao exam?

202
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:37,400
I know your family
is having difficulties.

203
00:13:37,719 --> 00:13:39,879
Maybe you should
explain your situation to the school?

204
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:42,719
Can I take the exam directly
if I don't come to school?

205
00:13:42,999 --> 00:13:44,839
Theoretically, yes.

206
00:13:45,239 --> 00:13:47,719
Gaokao is open to the entire society.

207
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:48,879
But...

208
00:13:48,879 --> 00:13:49,479
Bye, ma'am.

209
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:51,839
Unbelievable.

210
00:14:05,839 --> 00:14:06,879
Enjoy it.

211
00:14:17,839 --> 00:14:18,759
I'm heading to work.

212
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:55,200
Bai Shu? Bai Shu?

213
00:14:57,519 --> 00:14:58,080
Bai Shu?

214
00:15:00,359 --> 00:15:00,960
Bai Shu?

215
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,560
Xiaoming, Xiaoming.

216
00:15:05,999 --> 00:15:06,639
Here.

217
00:15:06,639 --> 00:15:07,280
Xiaoming.

218
00:15:07,719 --> 00:15:08,440
Here.

219
00:15:08,879 --> 00:15:11,040
Under the second flowerpot.
There's a key there.

220
00:15:11,599 --> 00:15:12,359
The white one?

221
00:16:30,519 --> 00:16:31,999
She won't let this go.

222
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:34,400
What can she do if you don't go home?

223
00:16:34,999 --> 00:16:36,080
It's only a few months.

224
00:16:36,239 --> 00:16:37,400
Just focus on studying.

225
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:40,440
Once you're in college,
she can't control you anymore.

226
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:45,359
You're worried about money?

227
00:16:47,719 --> 00:16:49,440
Even my mom can earn money.

228
00:16:49,440 --> 00:16:50,719
How could we not earn any?

229
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:52,239
I've already figured it out.

230
00:16:52,519 --> 00:16:53,879
We'll hold up a big sign

231
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,599
outside the Xinhua Bookstore.

232
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:56,856
It'll say

233
00:16:56,856 --> 00:16:59,119
'Elementary Homework Tutoring
Monthly Service.'

234
00:16:59,479 --> 00:17:00,759
Your grades are so good.

235
00:17:01,479 --> 00:17:02,999
You should earn at least 500 yuan.

236
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,799
My grades aren't as good.

237
00:17:07,719 --> 00:17:09,880
But earning 300 yuan
should be easy-peasy.

238
00:17:12,279 --> 00:17:13,600
Yeah, by then,

239
00:17:14,079 --> 00:17:15,120
we'll have 800 yuan.

240
00:17:15,719 --> 00:17:18,400
We can spend 150
to rent a room near the school.

241
00:17:19,360 --> 00:17:20,999
For food costs, we'll share meals.

242
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,559
At most, it costs 300 yuan.

243
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:25,039
Then we can save the rest of the money

244
00:17:25,239 --> 00:17:26,279
for travel expenses.

245
00:17:28,519 --> 00:17:30,200
She'll go to school looking for me.

246
00:17:30,559 --> 00:17:32,719
Just don't go to school. Problem solved.

247
00:17:32,759 --> 00:17:34,479
Didn't she already
ask for leave for you?

248
00:17:34,999 --> 00:17:37,079
Then you can just stay
in our rented room

249
00:17:37,279 --> 00:17:38,039
and study hard.

250
00:17:38,519 --> 00:17:39,479
I'll go to school

251
00:17:40,039 --> 00:17:41,319
and tell you what they teach.

252
00:17:47,719 --> 00:17:49,799
Right. You probably
don't even need me to do that.

253
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:55,279
Anyway, if she goes to see me at school,

254
00:17:55,279 --> 00:17:56,120
I'll just insist

255
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,719
that I don't know where you went.

256
00:17:57,960 --> 00:17:58,799
That's what I'll say.

257
00:17:59,079 --> 00:18:00,200
She can't eat me, right?

258
00:18:05,360 --> 00:18:07,960
Well, worst case,
I won't go to school either.

259
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:09,719
My mom can't afford the fee.

260
00:18:10,360 --> 00:18:12,120
We'll study together in that rented room

261
00:18:12,360 --> 00:18:14,239
and then just take the gaokao directly.

262
00:18:18,519 --> 00:18:19,960
Oh please, stop overthinking it.

263
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,239
Just listen to me, okay?

264
00:18:22,719 --> 00:18:23,519
What do we do now?

265
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,239
Let's go find some sponsors.

266
00:18:25,519 --> 00:18:26,799
We have reinforcements, okay?

267
00:18:28,440 --> 00:18:30,600
The thing is, we plan to move out.

268
00:18:31,200 --> 00:18:33,640
As for the reason,
if you're really my buddy, don't ask.

269
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,559
(Leather Jackets: All 70% Off)

270
00:18:34,559 --> 00:18:35,559
What do you two think?

271
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:37,640
Do you even need to rent?

272
00:18:37,840 --> 00:18:39,719
Who's my dad? He manages the market.

273
00:18:39,999 --> 00:18:41,200
It has plenty of empty places.

274
00:18:41,479 --> 00:18:42,239
We have the keys.

275
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,200
I'll get them.

276
00:18:43,759 --> 00:18:44,319
Bai Shu, here.

277
00:18:44,559 --> 00:18:45,999
It's cold. Wear something warmer.

278
00:18:46,712 --> 00:18:47,360
- No.
- Take it.

279
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:48,952
This isn't right. I can't.

280
00:18:48,952 --> 00:18:49,799
It's a gift. Take it.

281
00:18:49,799 --> 00:18:50,479
No, I can't.

282
00:18:50,640 --> 00:18:51,239
- I'll take it for you.
- What?

283
00:18:51,279 --> 00:18:51,799
No need.

284
00:18:51,999 --> 00:18:52,880
Just take it.

285
00:18:54,759 --> 00:18:55,719
You'll handle the place?

286
00:18:55,719 --> 00:18:56,360
Leave it to me.

287
00:18:56,719 --> 00:18:57,592
I'll handle the food.

288
00:18:57,999 --> 00:18:58,960
Don't be picky.

289
00:18:59,120 --> 00:19:00,360
It'll fill you up.

290
00:19:01,799 --> 00:19:04,079
See? Now you have food,
clothes, and a place to stay.

291
00:19:04,479 --> 00:19:05,719
You have friends who back you.

292
00:19:05,719 --> 00:19:07,039
What else are you worried about?

293
00:19:10,319 --> 00:19:11,719
That's so cool, you two.

294
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:12,559
Real friends.

295
00:19:13,144 --> 00:19:14,039
(All 70% Off)
Then let's go.

296
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:17,279
I'll bring you some food later.

297
00:19:17,600 --> 00:19:18,920
I want ribs with beans on rice.

298
00:19:19,079 --> 00:19:19,960
Got it.

299
00:19:30,559 --> 00:19:32,200
Boss, Ms. Ren,
who delivers buns, is here.

300
00:19:32,279 --> 00:19:33,400
She wants yesterday's pay.

301
00:19:38,719 --> 00:19:41,440
You go settle the bill with her.

302
00:19:41,440 --> 00:19:41,944
Okay.

303
00:19:42,279 --> 00:19:45,360
Then buy all her steamed buns
and throw them in the warehouse.

304
00:19:46,039 --> 00:19:47,279
Order a week's buns from her.

305
00:19:47,400 --> 00:19:48,120
Okay.

306
00:19:50,279 --> 00:19:52,400
Order a week's worth of rice
from Ms. Liu.

307
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:53,999
We'll be eating rice this week.

308
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:56,039
Rice for a week?

309
00:19:56,039 --> 00:19:57,039
Won't the buns go moldy

310
00:19:57,039 --> 00:19:57,999
in the warehouse?

311
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,920
We're just following orders.

312
00:20:01,160 --> 00:20:02,479
We'll do whatever they say.

313
00:20:02,999 --> 00:20:03,640
Don't pry.

314
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,600
Alright, I got it.

315
00:20:05,400 --> 00:20:06,360
Don't tell anyone else.

316
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:07,440
Two yuan for four.

317
00:20:07,960 --> 00:20:09,799
You hard workers need to eat more.

318
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:11,600
Ms. Ren,

319
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,640
let me pay yesterday's bill.

320
00:20:14,039 --> 00:20:15,999
I'll take whatever buns
are left from today.

321
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:17,799
And we want buns for a week, okay?

322
00:20:18,279 --> 00:20:19,120
Buns for a week?

323
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:20,039
Yes, buns for a week.

324
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,519
Thank you so much.

325
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,840
Thank you for that.

326
00:20:22,840 --> 00:20:23,960
You've been good to me.

327
00:20:24,079 --> 00:20:24,880
Here, two more buns.

328
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:25,799
Thanks, Ms. Ren.

329
00:20:25,799 --> 00:20:26,519
I don't have much.

330
00:20:26,519 --> 00:20:27,279
Thanks, Ms. Ren.

331
00:20:27,279 --> 00:20:28,079
I'll head back now.

332
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:29,640
Thank you so much.

333
00:20:31,279 --> 00:20:32,840
Buns for a week?

334
00:20:34,079 --> 00:20:36,039
I'm going to be rich.

335
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,192
You've been sitting here.
How'd you doze off?

336
00:21:24,440 --> 00:21:25,559
If I keep earning like this,

337
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,479
maybe in another month,

338
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:30,279
I will be able to scrape together
your sponsorship fee.

339
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,719
The school won't wait another month.

340
00:21:34,279 --> 00:21:34,920
Go to sleep.

341
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,719
We'll talk tomorrow.

342
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:37,680
Go to sleep.

343
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:39,840
It's so much.

344
00:21:41,719 --> 00:21:42,279
Go to sleep.

345
00:21:42,279 --> 00:21:42,840
Alright.

346
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:45,440
Take the stuff.

347
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,360
I'll be out in seconds.

348
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:47,960
In seconds.

349
00:21:54,999 --> 00:21:57,440
I'll talk to your teacher...
Where are you?

350
00:21:58,319 --> 00:22:00,039
I'll definitely pay the sponsorship fee.

351
00:22:00,120 --> 00:22:01,079
You don't need to worry.

352
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:02,319
Focus on your studies.

353
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:03,719
Stop fretting.

354
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,079
Go to sleep too.

355
00:22:12,360 --> 00:22:13,640
My little helper.

356
00:22:15,576 --> 00:22:16,120
Go to sleep.

357
00:22:16,120 --> 00:22:17,279
I'm going to sleep.

358
00:22:17,519 --> 00:22:18,200
Okay.

359
00:22:22,799 --> 00:22:23,519
Lights off.

360
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:26,039
Sure.

361
00:22:31,279 --> 00:22:31,799
Okay.

362
00:22:38,719 --> 00:22:39,279
Xiaoming.

363
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:42,680
Why don't you sleep yet?

364
00:22:43,608 --> 00:22:44,120
I will.

365
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,680
Why don't you sleep yet?

366
00:22:45,999 --> 00:22:47,279
I can't if you don't.

367
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:49,160
I can't if you don't.

368
00:22:49,840 --> 00:22:50,960
Then let's both go to sleep.

369
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:54,279
One, two, three.

370
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,120
Sleep.

371
00:23:50,936 --> 00:23:53,624
(One week later)

372
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:55,360
(Safe passage)
Two buns, alright.

373
00:23:55,719 --> 00:23:56,440
Okay, two.

374
00:23:56,600 --> 00:23:58,039
Coming, two.

375
00:23:58,519 --> 00:23:59,239
Stop selling.

376
00:23:59,239 --> 00:23:59,880
Two.

377
00:24:00,039 --> 00:24:00,640
Stop buying.

378
00:24:01,479 --> 00:24:01,999
Stop buying.

379
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:02,840
Put them here.

380
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:09,200
These buns are yours, right?

381
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,160
Yes.

382
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:14,120
So you're selling these rotten buns

383
00:24:14,319 --> 00:24:15,680
to cheat us workers?

384
00:24:16,519 --> 00:24:17,719
These aren't my buns.

385
00:24:17,719 --> 00:24:18,400
What do you mean?

386
00:24:18,479 --> 00:24:19,479
You just said they were.

387
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:20,640
They're yours.

388
00:24:21,559 --> 00:24:22,079
They are.

389
00:24:22,239 --> 00:24:23,200
These are my buns.

390
00:24:23,200 --> 00:24:24,999
I don't know
what's going on with these buns.

391
00:24:24,999 --> 00:24:26,479
You wretch, eat the buns!

392
00:24:26,759 --> 00:24:28,479
- Eat them!
- Eat them!

393
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:30,039
I... well...

394
00:24:30,039 --> 00:24:30,559
What...

395
00:24:30,559 --> 00:24:31,799
You eat my buns every day.

396
00:24:31,999 --> 00:24:33,479
My buns wouldn't be like this.

397
00:24:33,479 --> 00:24:35,360
I don't know why these are moldy.

398
00:24:35,479 --> 00:24:36,680
Don't listen to her nonsense.

399
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:39,279
Listen, take your buns and get lost.

400
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,559
- Get lost!
- Get lost!

401
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:42,759
- Get lost!
- Get lost!

402
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,120
Don't come back. Got it?

403
00:24:45,519 --> 00:24:46,920
- Get lost!
- Get lost!

404
00:24:47,039 --> 00:24:47,840
Don't come back.

405
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:48,600
Get lost!

406
00:24:49,120 --> 00:24:49,840
Get lost!

407
00:24:49,840 --> 00:24:50,640
Get lost!

408
00:24:50,840 --> 00:24:51,600
(Granny's Pickles)

409
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:52,200
Get lost!

410
00:24:53,120 --> 00:24:54,600
Get lost! Don't ever come back!

411
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,160
Get lost!

412
00:25:06,079 --> 00:25:06,999
Tell me the truth.

413
00:25:08,079 --> 00:25:10,360
Did you mix those spoiled buns
in with the good ones?

414
00:25:11,079 --> 00:25:12,400
I didn't, I swear.

415
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:14,200
I sell out of buns every day.

416
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,640
Where would I get spoiled buns?

417
00:25:18,079 --> 00:25:19,759
Then how did they get sick?

418
00:25:19,960 --> 00:25:21,160
Where are the bad buns from?

419
00:25:21,799 --> 00:25:22,880
How should I know?

420
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:26,120
I told you before

421
00:25:26,360 --> 00:25:28,360
to get a business license,
but you wouldn't.

422
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,160
Nothing happens? Fine.

423
00:25:30,799 --> 00:25:31,519
If something does,

424
00:25:31,840 --> 00:25:33,479
they'll bury you in fines.

425
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:34,880
Bury me in fines?

426
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:37,079
Would you be happy if I died?

427
00:25:39,680 --> 00:25:41,079
The workers won't let it go.

428
00:25:41,999 --> 00:25:43,120
The authority is fining me.

429
00:25:44,079 --> 00:25:45,680
I even borrowed to buy the equipment.

430
00:25:46,319 --> 00:25:47,840
How am I supposed to live?

431
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:53,239
When it comes down to it,

432
00:25:53,999 --> 00:25:55,120
isn't it all about money?

433
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:58,279
Just get the total amount
and pay it back slowly.

434
00:25:59,559 --> 00:26:01,519
You make it sound easy.
How will I repay it?

435
00:26:01,999 --> 00:26:04,400
None of the construction sites
in Qidaohezi want my buns now.

436
00:26:04,840 --> 00:26:06,319
Where can I find a livelihood?

437
00:26:22,840 --> 00:26:24,479
Maybe you could talk to Bai Shu.

438
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,079
Her mom has good connections.

439
00:26:26,759 --> 00:26:27,759
Don't think about it.

440
00:26:28,319 --> 00:26:29,559
If you dare tell Bai Shu,

441
00:26:29,880 --> 00:26:31,160
I'm cutting ties with you.

442
00:26:32,719 --> 00:26:33,920
Are you crazy?

443
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:36,160
Why not ask a good friend for help?

444
00:26:36,559 --> 00:26:38,400
Are you ashamed
of me in front of your friend?

445
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:39,519
Cutting ties?

446
00:26:39,719 --> 00:26:41,360
Who am I earning money to support?

447
00:26:42,120 --> 00:26:43,352
Who's the sponsorship fee for?

448
00:26:43,719 --> 00:26:44,880
If you want to cut ties, go.

449
00:26:45,079 --> 00:26:45,920
Fine, I'm leaving.

450
00:27:15,479 --> 00:27:16,400
Have some water.

451
00:27:30,079 --> 00:27:31,640
What are you thinking about, Ms. Zhou?

452
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:43,360
I'm heading back soon

453
00:27:45,799 --> 00:27:46,880
to fight a tough battle.

454
00:27:48,920 --> 00:27:49,920
After that,

455
00:27:53,360 --> 00:27:55,200
I may not get another chance to see you.

456
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,840
Actually, I have a big secret.

457
00:28:02,840 --> 00:28:04,079
It involves you.

458
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:06,960
But I haven't told anyone.

459
00:28:08,440 --> 00:28:09,079
(Excuse me.)

460
00:28:09,079 --> 00:28:09,640
(Come in.)

461
00:28:09,848 --> 00:28:12,999
(Qidaohezi Qidian Middle School, 2004)

462
00:28:12,999 --> 00:28:15,079
Bai Shu? Ren Xiaoming?

463
00:28:15,799 --> 00:28:16,960
What brings you two here?

464
00:28:17,319 --> 00:28:18,319
- Ms. Wang.
- Ms. Wang.

465
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:20,479
You're here to see Ms. Zhou, right?

466
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:25,840
The day she left,
I happened to run into Ms. Zhou.

467
00:28:28,239 --> 00:28:28,960
Ms. Wang.

468
00:28:32,079 --> 00:28:33,319
Previous class graduates,

469
00:28:33,479 --> 00:28:35,440
Bai Shu and Ren Xiaoming.
Do you remember them?

470
00:28:37,719 --> 00:28:39,440
If they come to school looking for me,

471
00:28:40,160 --> 00:28:42,640
please give them this pen.

472
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:46,079
(At that critical moment,)

473
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:48,319
(you still thought to leave us the pen.)

474
00:28:49,920 --> 00:28:52,160
(We received your wish.)

475
00:28:54,559 --> 00:28:55,799
(But later...)

476
00:28:56,559 --> 00:28:58,799
I lost the pen you gave us.

477
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:05,920
I'm sorry.

478
00:29:11,799 --> 00:29:12,600
I'm sorry.

479
00:29:14,920 --> 00:29:15,519
I'm sorry.

480
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,200
Were you trying to say

481
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:45,640
courage is in my heart?

482
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,640
Bai Shu?

483
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,840
Ms. Zhou, Bai Shu is here to see you.

484
00:30:18,239 --> 00:30:18,920
I'll go get her.

485
00:30:41,784 --> 00:30:42,799
(Qidaohezi, 2006)

486
00:30:42,799 --> 00:30:44,440
One awful thing after another.

487
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:45,999
Never mind how old I am.

488
00:30:46,360 --> 00:30:47,719
I feel like I've aged.

489
00:30:48,600 --> 00:30:50,120
Aged? Let me see.

490
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:52,079
A little bit.

491
00:30:52,799 --> 00:30:53,559
What's going on?

492
00:30:54,519 --> 00:30:55,239
It's nothing.

493
00:30:57,999 --> 00:31:00,319
It's been over ten days.
Ge Wenjun hasn't come to you.

494
00:31:00,719 --> 00:31:01,719
Or me.

495
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,799
Did she really let you off?

496
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:06,079
I don't know.

497
00:31:07,559 --> 00:31:08,759
It's better if she hasn't.

498
00:31:09,239 --> 00:31:11,559
Just study diligently.
Don't be afraid of anything.

499
00:31:11,719 --> 00:31:12,519
We're here for you.

500
00:31:14,079 --> 00:31:15,479
I now rely on you for everything.

501
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:18,239
I'm just a huge burden.

502
00:31:19,079 --> 00:31:20,680
You are not a burden.

503
00:31:21,319 --> 00:31:23,479
The three of us
are counting on you to tutor us.

504
00:31:23,680 --> 00:31:25,440
We're the ones exploiting you.

505
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,200
You're comforting me.

506
00:31:29,319 --> 00:31:31,079
Who has time to comfort you?

507
00:31:37,239 --> 00:31:39,680
Didn't He Yuqiong say he'd
bring the living expenses today?

508
00:31:39,680 --> 00:31:40,519
Where is he?

509
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,288
Mom?

510
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:45,519
Are you alright?

511
00:31:47,279 --> 00:31:48,759
He took everything this time.

512
00:31:49,079 --> 00:31:50,719
He didn't leave a single cent.

513
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:02,840
Here, take this money.

514
00:32:23,920 --> 00:32:25,400
It's okay. I'm here.

515
00:32:30,279 --> 00:32:32,759
(500 Yuan Prize)
Xingfu Road Bakery Eating Challenge.

516
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:34,799
We're still missing one last contestant.

517
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:37,319
This is an opportunity not to be missed!

518
00:32:37,999 --> 00:32:38,840
(500 Yuan Prize)
I'll count down from five.

519
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:42,232
(500 Yuan Prize)
Five, four, three,

520
00:32:42,319 --> 00:32:43,880
two, one!

521
00:32:44,559 --> 00:32:45,752
Me! Me!

522
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:46,759
Me! Me! Me!

523
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:47,640
Good!

524
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,920
(Bakery Eating Challenge)
Alright,

525
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:52,479
our final contestant for the challenge
has arrived!

526
00:32:52,680 --> 00:32:53,239
Go on over.

527
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:55,920
Let me go over the rules
of this challenge again.

528
00:32:56,160 --> 00:32:57,239
The rules are simple.

529
00:32:57,559 --> 00:32:59,799
Eat three kilograms
of our 'Sweet Little Cake'

530
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,519
in one go, and you win.

531
00:33:01,719 --> 00:33:03,319
The winner gets the title 'Big Eater'

532
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:05,840
and a cash prize of 500 yuan.

533
00:33:05,999 --> 00:33:06,880
Great!

534
00:33:07,120 --> 00:33:07,999
- Great!
- Great!

535
00:33:08,559 --> 00:33:09,680
What if they can't finish?

536
00:33:10,079 --> 00:33:11,319
Not finishing isn't a big deal.

537
00:33:11,479 --> 00:33:12,920
Pay me for however much they eat.

538
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:17,528
Xingfu Road Bakery Eating Challenge

539
00:33:17,528 --> 00:33:18,872
begins now.

540
00:33:20,079 --> 00:33:20,759
Go!

541
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:21,640
Go!

542
00:33:21,799 --> 00:33:25,479
- Go! Go!
- Go!

543
00:33:25,719 --> 00:33:26,719
Puking doesn't count.

544
00:33:27,279 --> 00:33:28,319
If you puke, pay me.

545
00:33:28,559 --> 00:33:32,719
(500 Yuan Prize)
Go! Go! Go!

546
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:40,400
Buddy, can't eat anymore?

547
00:33:40,719 --> 00:33:41,960
You puked. You have to pay me.

548
00:33:42,319 --> 00:33:43,479
Come inside and pay me.

549
00:33:43,559 --> 00:33:44,640
Pay up! Pay up!

550
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:50,559
(500 Yuan Prize)
Don't run!

551
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:51,920
Come back! Come back!

552
00:33:53,496 --> 00:33:55,064
(Bakery Eating Challenge)

553
00:33:56,440 --> 00:33:58,168
(500 Yuan Prize)

554
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,519
Puking doesn't count.

555
00:34:14,519 --> 00:34:15,119
Go for it!

556
00:34:15,199 --> 00:34:16,280
Puking doesn't count.

557
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:23,760
Can he still eat?

558
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:27,360
I'm counting from five.

559
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,599
Only counts if he holds.

560
00:34:28,599 --> 00:34:30,360
Five, four,

561
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:33,760
three, two, one!

562
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:36,119
Pay up.

563
00:34:36,119 --> 00:34:36,840
Yeah.

564
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:37,960
He finished it.

565
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:38,960
I declare

566
00:34:39,119 --> 00:34:42,440
the Xingfu Road Bakery Eating Challenge
has a winner!

567
00:34:45,079 --> 00:34:45,800
See?

568
00:34:46,079 --> 00:34:47,679
The shiny 500 yuan!

569
00:34:47,768 --> 00:34:48,559
(Cakes, Bread, Bakery)

570
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:49,760
- Good!
- Good!

571
00:34:55,119 --> 00:34:57,360
I'm speechless. He's so unreliable.

572
00:35:02,599 --> 00:35:03,479
What? Hungry?

573
00:35:04,559 --> 00:35:05,199
A bit.

574
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:07,639
It's been a whole day. Just 'a bit'?

575
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:12,639
Alright, go back to the market
and wait for me.

576
00:35:13,079 --> 00:35:14,159
I'll go home and see

577
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,360
what I can find for you.

578
00:35:17,159 --> 00:35:18,840
Stop dawdling. Get going.

579
00:35:34,840 --> 00:35:35,760
Xiaoming, you're back.

580
00:35:39,479 --> 00:35:40,639
What are you doing?

581
00:35:41,119 --> 00:35:41,999
Nothing.

582
00:35:42,440 --> 00:35:43,679
Nothing? What are you doing?

583
00:35:44,800 --> 00:35:46,679
I'm looking for a book.

584
00:35:54,119 --> 00:35:54,960
Are you going out?

585
00:35:56,079 --> 00:35:57,079
Going to self-study.

586
00:35:58,240 --> 00:35:59,760
Didn't you just get back from school?

587
00:36:00,920 --> 00:36:02,479
The teacher told me to go back.

588
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:04,240
It's almost dinnertime. Time to cook.

589
00:36:04,240 --> 00:36:05,079
Where are you going?

590
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,079
Can't you just study at home?

591
00:36:08,880 --> 00:36:10,999
No, the teacher said to go to school.

592
00:36:19,240 --> 00:36:20,479
Where exactly is she going?

593
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,119
I'm back.

594
00:36:35,159 --> 00:36:36,320
Scoot over.

595
00:36:41,479 --> 00:36:42,240
Where's Bai Shu?

596
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:43,720
Went to buy food.

597
00:36:45,639 --> 00:36:46,840
Did you give her the money?

598
00:36:52,079 --> 00:36:53,679
What's going on with you?

599
00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:55,999
Why did you give her the money so late?

600
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:58,639
Bai Shu wouldn't tell us
if she ran out of food.

601
00:36:58,999 --> 00:36:59,880
It's been a whole day.

602
00:37:01,159 --> 00:37:03,720
If you couldn't do it,
you shouldn't have promised.

603
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:13,079
Why are you sleeping in during the day?

604
00:37:15,639 --> 00:37:17,079
Alright, get up and do homework.

605
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,240
What's wrong?

606
00:37:24,079 --> 00:37:24,880
Feeling unwell?

607
00:37:25,240 --> 00:37:25,800
I'm fine.

608
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:26,440
What's wrong?

609
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:28,760
Where does it hurt?

610
00:37:29,599 --> 00:37:31,159
Why do you look so pale?

611
00:37:33,079 --> 00:37:33,880
Are you sick?

612
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:35,760
Ren Xiaoming.

613
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:41,519
Why are you here?

614
00:37:42,159 --> 00:37:42,679
Don't...

615
00:37:43,720 --> 00:37:46,440
Why are you here? Get out.

616
00:37:49,240 --> 00:37:50,159
- What?
- Get up.

617
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:50,920
It's my mom.

618
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:51,999
It's my mom.

619
00:37:52,079 --> 00:37:53,479
He Yuqiong, get up. Hurry.

620
00:37:53,479 --> 00:37:54,639
Get up now.

621
00:37:54,760 --> 00:37:56,079
I tried so hard to stop this.

622
00:37:56,519 --> 00:37:58,159
But you two still ended up together.

623
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,760
You're a girl!

624
00:37:59,840 --> 00:38:00,840
I'll beat you to death!

625
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:02,320
Ma'am!

626
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,159
Stop hitting him!

627
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:05,159
- He Yuqiong!
- You ruined my daughter!

628
00:38:05,280 --> 00:38:06,320
You ruined my daughter!

629
00:38:06,880 --> 00:38:07,999
Get up, He Yuqiong!

630
00:38:08,079 --> 00:38:08,720
Go quickly!

631
00:38:09,159 --> 00:38:10,360
Don't just lie there!

632
00:38:11,519 --> 00:38:12,280
You're a boy.

633
00:38:12,559 --> 00:38:13,440
Stop hitting him!

634
00:38:13,479 --> 00:38:14,479
You ruined my daughter!

635
00:38:16,519 --> 00:38:17,400
Where are you going?

636
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:18,720
Explain yourself!

637
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:19,800
You ruined her!

638
00:38:19,960 --> 00:38:20,840
Stop it!

639
00:38:21,639 --> 00:38:22,360
Hurry! Hurry!

640
00:38:22,999 --> 00:38:24,159
Go! Go now!

641
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,079
Stop!

642
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:27,400
Go!

643
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:28,479
We're settling this today!

644
00:38:28,999 --> 00:38:32,079
Explain! Explain yourself!

645
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:32,760
You!

646
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,720
Stop it!

647
00:38:35,079 --> 00:38:36,280
Stop hitting him!

648
00:38:37,159 --> 00:38:38,599
Explain yourself!

649
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,360
Stop it!

650
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,679
Explain yourself!

651
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,240
You both explain it!

652
00:38:50,559 --> 00:38:51,079
He Yuqiong?

653
00:38:52,079 --> 00:38:53,119
Get up. Get up.

654
00:38:53,159 --> 00:38:53,720
Hurry. Hurry.

655
00:38:55,999 --> 00:38:56,880
Your hands are cold.

656
00:38:57,528 --> 00:38:58,168
He Yuqiong?

657
00:38:58,872 --> 00:39:00,079
Why is he twitching?

658
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,720
You beat him to death!

659
00:39:02,320 --> 00:39:04,280
I barely hit him. He fell himself.

660
00:39:05,240 --> 00:39:06,760
You killed him!

661
00:39:07,079 --> 00:39:07,800
What happened?

662
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:10,159
- My mom beat He Yuqiong to death.
- Why are you here?

663
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:12,760
He fell down himself. I...

664
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,360
He's alive. Call an ambulance.

665
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,360
Call the police.

666
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,679
Call an ambulance!

667
00:39:17,199 --> 00:39:18,079
Call the police!

668
00:39:18,079 --> 00:39:18,960
Call an ambulance!

669
00:39:19,079 --> 00:39:20,119
Call an ambulance, ma'am!

670
00:39:20,119 --> 00:39:21,280
Call the police!

671
00:39:21,599 --> 00:39:22,639
Call an ambulance!

672
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,519
Call an ambulance!

673
00:39:23,519 --> 00:39:24,240
Call an ambulance!

674
00:39:24,504 --> 00:39:25,159
The ambulance.

675
00:39:25,159 --> 00:39:25,679
He Yuqiong?

676
00:39:26,104 --> 00:39:27,199
I take him to the hospital.

677
00:39:27,519 --> 00:39:29,199
Enough! Stop wasting time.

678
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:30,440
Call an ambulance.

679
00:39:32,199 --> 00:39:32,720
Hurry! Hurry!

680
00:39:33,639 --> 00:39:35,159
Hello? I need an ambulance.

681
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:37,119
Hurry! Open the door!

682
00:39:37,119 --> 00:39:37,840
Let's go.

683
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:05,440
You're finally awake.

684
00:40:05,720 --> 00:40:06,760
You scared us to death.

685
00:40:09,599 --> 00:40:10,199
And your mom?

686
00:40:10,999 --> 00:40:11,639
She's outside.

687
00:40:12,240 --> 00:40:13,119
You need to leave.

688
00:40:13,360 --> 00:40:15,920
If your mom sees me with you later,

689
00:40:15,920 --> 00:40:16,760
she'll beat me again.

690
00:40:18,999 --> 00:40:20,519
They asked me to watch over you.

691
00:40:22,280 --> 00:40:23,960
You can't be left alone right now.

692
00:40:26,519 --> 00:40:28,639
Do you know you almost died just now?

693
00:40:33,720 --> 00:40:34,920
Why is my head so dizzy?

694
00:40:34,920 --> 00:40:36,119
It feels stuffed with paste.

695
00:40:36,519 --> 00:40:37,679
Well, no wonder.

696
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:39,999
Your stomach was about to burst earlier.

697
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:42,199
They had to pump and flush it.

698
00:40:44,599 --> 00:40:45,679
Of course, you feel awful.

699
00:40:47,479 --> 00:40:48,920
Why did you eat so many pastries?

700
00:40:51,360 --> 00:40:54,119
Three kilos to win 500 yuan.

701
00:40:55,639 --> 00:40:57,199
Aren't you stupid?

702
00:40:57,320 --> 00:40:58,800
Your life is only worth 500 yuan?

703
00:40:59,119 --> 00:41:00,679
That's just a marketing gimmick.

704
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,960
He Youliang came home today
and took all the money.

705
00:41:03,880 --> 00:41:05,920
I promised to cover the food.
I must keep my word.

706
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:07,840
Don't tell Bai Shu that.

707
00:41:07,999 --> 00:41:09,159
So she won't feel burdened.

708
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,320
Just say I was showing off
and bet someone.

709
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:15,320
That was one expensive bet you made.

710
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:17,720
IV fluids, stomach pumping,

711
00:41:18,079 --> 00:41:19,199
plus your bed fee,

712
00:41:19,639 --> 00:41:20,679
have cost over 2,000 yuan.

713
00:41:20,999 --> 00:41:22,519
Then let's go. I can't afford that.

714
00:41:22,599 --> 00:41:23,400
We don't have money.

715
00:41:23,559 --> 00:41:24,360
Sit down.

716
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:27,079
My mom paid the money.

717
00:41:28,559 --> 00:41:30,679
Then, tell your mom
that I'll pay her back.

718
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,639
You haven't told my mom, right?

719
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:35,840
Haven't had the time yet.

720
00:41:36,280 --> 00:41:37,479
As buddies, keep it a secret.

721
00:41:39,240 --> 00:41:41,079
You need to stay here today
for observation.

722
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:42,479
There's no way to hide it.

723
00:41:43,240 --> 00:41:44,920
Then I need to hurry back. I...

724
00:41:45,199 --> 00:41:45,880
Lie down.

725
00:41:46,960 --> 00:41:47,720
Alright.

726
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:50,119
I'll tell your mom

727
00:41:51,519 --> 00:41:53,840
that we'll stay up late
doing tests today.

728
00:41:55,559 --> 00:41:56,559
No.

729
00:41:56,760 --> 00:41:58,840
My mom's been at the stall all day.
She needs rest.

730
00:41:58,840 --> 00:41:59,400
I must go.

731
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:00,119
Lie down.

732
00:42:00,519 --> 00:42:02,199
Just have Zhang Fang watch the stall.

733
00:42:02,400 --> 00:42:04,159
What can Zhang Fang possibly do?

734
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:07,679
If you leave today, we're done.

735
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:08,360
Got it?

736
00:42:09,039 --> 00:42:09,960
What are you doing?

737
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:13,639
Looking after him.

738
00:42:15,240 --> 00:42:15,999
Hello, ma'am.

739
00:42:18,479 --> 00:42:19,479
You come out. Hurry.

740
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:22,079
Come out.

741
00:42:37,519 --> 00:42:39,840
Xiaoming, I told your mom everything.

742
00:42:43,999 --> 00:42:44,999
Everything?

743
00:42:46,679 --> 00:42:47,400
Everything.

744
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:50,280
You even told her
you're not the real Bai Shu?

745
00:42:54,800 --> 00:42:56,240
Why did you have to tell her?

746
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:57,679
She can't keep a secret.

747
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:58,639
Shut it.

748
00:42:59,119 --> 00:42:59,960
I can keep a secret.

749
00:43:00,800 --> 00:43:02,240
How can you say that about me?

750
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:12,808
=Vanished Name=
